&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Traeger is looking for a passionate, people-first Retail Sales Specialist to represent our brand across national chain retail accounts in the Salt Lake area. As the face of Traeger in your region, you&#39;ll build lasting relationships with retail partners, educate and inspire store associates, and bring new fans into the Traegerhood — one cook at a time.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a dynamic, field-based role perfect for someone who thrives on variety, loves being out of the office, and is energized by connecting with people. Expect regular weekend activations, occasional overnight travel, and a front-row seat to one of the most passionate communities in outdoor cooking.&lt;/p&gt;
